                    <div class="discussion-question">
                        <h3>Nature of Evil</h3>
                        <p>Do you believe evil people are born evil or made evil by circumstances? Can ordinary people commit terrible acts?</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="discussion-question">
                        <h3>Following Orders</h3>
                        <p>Is "I was just following orders" ever a valid excuse? When should people refuse to obey authority?</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="discussion-question">
                        <h3>Bureaucracy and Responsibility</h3>
                        <p>How can bureaucratic systems make people less responsible for their actions? Have you experienced this?</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="discussion-question">
                        <h3>Modern Applications</h3>
                        <p>Where do you see examples of "the banality of evil" in today's world? How can we prevent it?</p>
                    </div>
